message.body: I just sent the ######## story over to your #### email. If you can get to it today, awesome, but no worries if not! Have a good trip tomorrow.
Hey! Great story! Did you have a suggestion for a headline? Just wanted to check....
I really gotta work on headline writing. Writers never write them, editors always do. I'm out of practice! Whatever you think is best. Next time I'll have one!
